Package: cl-lml2
Version: 1.5.1
Revision: 1
Description: Lisp Markup Language
License: LGPL
Maintainer: Lars Rosengreen <lars@margay.org>

Type: cl

Depends: clc, clisp-clc | cmucl-clc | openmcl-clc | sbcl-clc ,cl-kmrcl

Source: http://files.b9.com/lml2/lml2-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 6cbb151957e3e395b6e48b3b99fe7c7a

SourceDirectory: lml2-%v

CompileScript: /usr/bin/true

InstallScript: <<
  find . -type d -exec chmod 755 {} \;
  find . -type f -exec chmod 644 {} \;
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/source/lml2
  cp -Rp * %i/share/common-lisp/source/lml2
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/systems
  ln -s %p/share/common-lisp/source/lml2/lml2.asd %i/share/common-lisp/systems/lml2.asd
<<

PostInstScript: %p/sbin/register-common-lisp-source lml2
PreRmScript: %p/sbin/unregister-common-lisp-source lml2

DocFiles: ChangeLog LICENSE README doc/readme.html

DescDetail: << 
A Common Lisp package for generating HTML and XHTML documents.
<<

DescUsage: <<
(require "asdf")
(require "lml2")
<<

Homepage: http://lml2.b9.com/

